abstracts.cdata!:
The project would involve: improvement
            or construction of: (a) Damascus-Lebanese border highway (b)
            Damascus-Jordanian border highway, and (c) Tall Kalakh
            detour on the Homs-Tartous highway (ii) technical assistance
            consisting in consultants' services for: (a)
            supervision of above works, (b) preparation of feasibility
            studies and, if justified, detailed engineering for about
            540 km of further road work, and (c) bringing up to date a
            study on road maintenance needs.
